    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a really solid start. i like the phrasing. can u expand on that? like, how should i address the counter-argument about meritocracy? people usually say that wealth should just come from hard work/talent. how can i frame that argument as being fundamentally flawed or even harmful to progress in the paper?",
